  "content": "<div class=\"slide-inner\">\n    <div class=\"slide-label\">The Bootstrap</div>\n    <div class=\"slide-title\">Day 1: <span class=\"hl-amber\">No Tool Yet</span></div>\n    <div class=\"slide-subtitle\">Building a memory system that can't remember anything. Yet.</div>\n    <div class=\"timeline\">\n      <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-marker\">\n          <div class=\"timeline-dot\" style=\"background: var(--accent-amber);\"></div>\n          <div class=\"timeline-line\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n          <h3>Markdown files</h3>\n          <p>Asked Claude to save every decision in a specific format. Brainstorms, trade-offs, architecture calls. All by hand. The plan: migrate it all once the tool is ready.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-marker\">\n          <div class=\"timeline-dot\" style=\"background: var(--accent-blue);\"></div>\n          <div class=\"timeline-line\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n          <h3>Obra's superpowers plugin</h3>\n          <p>The brainstorming skill structured every design session. Explore, clarify, converge. This was the process from day 1. The rest came later.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-marker\">\n          <div class=\"timeline-dot\" style=\"background: var(--accent-green);\"></div>\n          <div class=\"timeline-line\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n          <h3>First self-ingest</h3>\n          <p>corvia ingests its own decisions. The markdown files migrate in. Now the tool can search its own history. The loop starts forming.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-marker\">\n          <div class=\"timeline-dot\" style=\"background: var(--accent-purple);\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n          <h3>The loop gets better</h3>\n          <p>5-persona review, session history, agent coordination. The process and the product grew together.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      <span>Lim Chun Zhe</span>\n      <span>4 / 10</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
